Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry?  K
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pard？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  总是让女人救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么突然来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤之王有话传给黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心局域网闹事份子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不直接跟她说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能更有趣一些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是疑问语气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没问题  问题可大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知集合的邮件上只写着有要事几个字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐肯定是生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安  有田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听公主说过了  你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是要商量些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  你不用招呼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田很喜欢对人道歉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不得不道歉的情况比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  公主似乎从早上起心情就不是太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪公主学姐怎么会因为我而不高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田总是叫公主做学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说  我稍微有点妒忌你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直以来  和公主直连以及一起上学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出现之后就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了  若宫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和黑雪公主学姐的关系  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话就是利害一致
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像弟子和老师那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概没有私人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是一点私人感情都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我们迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事去了老师办公室一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们叫来不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有事想拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实最近在校园局域网内发生了某起事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有听说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…阿千呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  仁子有话让我转达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容是小心局域网闹事份子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  阿春  你和赤之王一直保持联络？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  刚才Pard让我转达的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  还坐到人家摩托车的后座了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样没错  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会我再问问她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定除了梅乡中学以外也有事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以外的意思是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  有学生在放学后被留在了校园局域网
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(215,328)}Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚拟角色的衣服和物品都被人扒光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿盔甲和拿枪的南瓜头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  还攻破了禁止过分接触的系统限制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是学姐  为什么要和我们说这事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  对方好像使用了系统外的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果属实的话  仅靠学生会成员恐怕应付不来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次  如果事情闹大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能引来有关部门的干预
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令当前学生会的权限受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尽可能地避免这个事态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟有可能再次发生像能美那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后第三  我最信赖的就是你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚拟角色抢劫绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会尽力帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然也会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春…也不用问了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是遵循学姐的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间定在放学之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了  拓武  千百合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生虚拟角色抢劫的果然不仅我们学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但从收集到的情报来看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻而易举地入侵防御坚固的学校网络
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不留一点痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就黑客来说可是个高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做的仅仅是扒光虚拟角色的衣服和物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法和目的之间不对等  反而令人觉得可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这次就是我多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  感谢你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人情你要我怎么还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  那就把Silver  Crow让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他可能在你那边才有更好的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑  给我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人  到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上月同学  方便的话能帮忙搬一下教材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老师  我很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅乡中学校园局域网统一下线时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请对文件进行保存  退出连线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  阿春你今天真安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从早上起  就让她看到很多出糗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是乎黑雪公主学姐好像生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了？  我看上去不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像…是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  再说我了解女人心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会吃那么多苦头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊  女孩子真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千百合  唐突地问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待人的态度很强硬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会令人很紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪在我面前总是畏畏缩缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着也觉得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐确实说不上很容易相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  果然是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是阿春的问题更严重些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick  or  Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你哦  南瓜灯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  你这个大南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能在FPS领域里认输
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  身体好轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  阿千你没事就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这个空间重力很小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该不是校园局域网吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千你快点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你想说我很重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到Accel  Assault
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫DShK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(359,328)}Assault  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一名火力连线者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力连线者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了  我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Assault  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力连线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时钟停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  快想象自己的虚拟角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐好美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和Brain  Burst不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个空间也由类似的法则支配
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你们精神不够集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(346,328)}Elemental  Bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤  元素子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  快用我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(301,328)}Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  刚开始就用必杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(340,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——快枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畅快！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接着去攻击本体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Splash  Stinger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞针四射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费弹药了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Splash  Stinger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞针四射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千…弹药…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没弹药了  让我休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀  真没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春你也怎么了  老发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的盘旋速度并不是很快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用机动力决一胜负的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉军团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…就这种程度学姐应该早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着我特意去告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只是知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是有什么应对的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去学姐那里  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐始终是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也希望有男孩子能帮助自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动地和自己说话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  左边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是学姐也能在空中自由移动的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我再也不让你吃我妈妈做的饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  阿拓  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅靠物理攻击力是打不赢她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要看清她移动的破绽  迅速展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之  要瞄准她盘旋的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是低重力空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在空中可是对她有利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来成为学姐的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…学姐请专注物理攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于肯当面和我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么小的翅膀可能帮不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个空间和Brain  Burst一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象力——心念在这里也能发挥效用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此想象将会成为你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你渴望的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所渴望的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和学姐一起翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的翅膀翱翔  原来是那么畅快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军团长  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间正在崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是传送门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:22:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没油了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再加一把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我在想她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DShK她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人觉得有点伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不再有人登陆的服务器里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待着对战对手出现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后就像丧失人气的游戏终止运营一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  在我打倒她的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种游戏通关之后  带着不舍的满足感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当时一定也是这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后合体的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你好像想挑战什么  可是随后又放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  那只是一时情急
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.39,0:24:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是考验下我的胆量…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  等我有一天有了那份自信之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.66,0:24:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我直接叫你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.89,0:24:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫学姐你的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.36,0:24:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  在那之前我都是黑雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.44,0:24:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯


